node.title: Traffic chaos for Aucklanders heading north as tree blocks section of SH1
node.description: Stop/go traffic management is in place.
node.content: ["Aucklanders heading north ahead of New Year\u2019s Eve celebrations are being warned to expect delays after a tree fell on a northbound section of State Highway 1.", "Those heading south can also expect delays with the section of the road just north of Johnstones Hill tunnel down to stop/go sign traffic management.", "Waka Kotahi said in an update just before 8am stop/go signs will need to be used in the area for some time as response crews work to clear the road.\u00a0\u00a0", "Motorists should expect 10 to 15 min delays northbound between Silverdale and Puhoi.\u00a0"]
